{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Karlach reacts to Wyll's OM confronting her.",
    "how_to_trigger": "Make Wyll join, leave, or kill him after CAMP_WyllConfrontation_IVB_CFM or CAMP_WyllConfrontation_NotRecruited_CFM"
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "22": {
      "id": "22",
      "speaker": "Karlach",
      "text": "Glad Wyll saw sense. Even more glad he decided to stick around. Takes a pretty slick mover to track down ol' Karlach.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "ORI_Karlach_IPRD_WyllJoinsAfterConfrontation"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "24",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "40": {
          "id": "40",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Does it? You're pretty loud.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "4": {
              "id": "4",
              "speaker": "Karlach",
              "text": "Fair. But still, the man's got a reputation for being lethal with that blade. I'm glad it's on our side.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": true,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "28": {
          "id": "28",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I'm glad he's joined us, too. Glad you two could make peace.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "11": {
              "id": "11",
              "speaker": "Karlach",
              "text": "Same. Now, instead of a liability, I've got a friend. Or - I will have soon, anyway.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Showing her hand as being a little kid-like and eager to make friends. Then catching herself like 'well, maybe just acquaintances now, but friends soon :) '",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": true,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "16": {
          "id": "16",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I'm keeping an eye on him. If he turns on you again, he's dead.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "34": {
              "id": "34",
              "speaker": "Karlach",
              "text": "He won't. Someone wrong-footed him about me, and I'm betting we'll find out who before long.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "9": {
                  "id": "9",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "I respect someone who can admit when they're wrong. And stick around after, too. Plus, did you see his eye? Bet there's a good story there.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": true,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {}
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "27": {
      "id": "27",
      "speaker": "Karlach",
      "text": "Blade. Glad we've decided to see eye to eye. I wouldn't really want you for an enemy, you know.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "REALLY_WYLL"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "24",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "26": {
          "id": "26",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Nor I, you.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "29": {
              "id": "29",
              "speaker": "Karlach",
              "text": "Well, looks like we've got the mutual respect secured. Next stop: friends.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": true,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "5": {
          "id": "5",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I should've known better from the start. But I know now.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "17": {
              "id": "17",
              "speaker": "Karlach",
              "text": "Water under the bridge, as far as I'm concerned. Looking forward to working with you, Wyll.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": true,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "32": {
          "id": "32",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Don't make me regret my decision.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "18": {
              "id": "18",
              "speaker": "Karlach",
              "text": "You, you'll regret it. When I've got all your gear strapped to my back and you grow soft and spoiled, you'll regret it.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": true,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "30": {
      "id": "30",
      "speaker": "Karlach",
      "text": "Tsk. Pity about Wyll. He would've made a good ally. Tracked me down pretty handily - that takes skill.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "ORI_Karlach_IPRD_WyllLeavesAfterConfrontation"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "24",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "21": {
          "id": "21",
          "speaker": "Karlach",
          "text": "Why'd you send him away?",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "24",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "35": {
              "id": "35",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Someone set him after you. I don't want to get tangled up with whoever that is.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "24",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "14": {
                  "id": "14",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "That's fair. I assumed it was Zariel, but he seemed to hate devils as much as I do.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "37": {
                      "id": "37",
                      "speaker": "Karlach",
                      "text": "Maybe this means I've got another, different target on my back. Goodie!",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": true,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "3": {
              "id": "3",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Can't have a monster hunter on the team. I'm a bit of a monster myself.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "24",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "6": {
                  "id": "6",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "Why do I find that hard to believe?",
                  "context": "NodeContext: A bit warmly, toward the player, who just called themselves a monster.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "24",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {}
                }
              }
            },
            "2": {
              "id": "2",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I just took a dislike to him. Nothing more.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "1": {
                  "id": "1",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "Really? I liked him. Dedicated, but not fanatical. Bet that eye had a good story behind it, too.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "24": {
                      "id": "24",
                      "speaker": "Karlach",
                      "text": "Well, may the Blade of Frontiers fight evil on his own time, then. And may he smite only the most deservingest of vermin.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": true,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "0": {
              "id": "0",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I just feel like we wouldn't have got along.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [
                "REALLY_ASTARION"
              ],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "33": {
                  "id": "33",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "Can't imagine why. You're sound, he's sound. You've got a tadpole, he's got a tadpole. Like jam and scones.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "39": {
                      "id": "39",
                      "speaker": "",
                      "text": "",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "24",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "jump",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "15": {
              "id": "15",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I suspect he and I would not have seen eye to eye.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [
                "REALLY_DARK_URGE"
              ],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "10": {
                  "id": "10",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "Where's the clash? You're both sound operators with tadpoles in your heads. But - the decision's made.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "13": {
                      "id": "13",
                      "speaker": "Karlach",
                      "text": "May the Blade of Frontiers fight evil on his own time, then. And may he smite only the most deservingest of vermin.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": true,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "36": {
      "id": "36",
      "speaker": "Karlach",
      "text": "Fucking Blade of Frontiers! He's supposed to hunt monsters, not... not me.",
      "context": "NodeContext: Wyll died during the confrontation; Karlach is sad it came to that.",
      "checkflags": [
        "ORI_Karlach_IPRD_WyllDiesAfterConfrontation"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "20",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "8": {
          "id": "8",
          "speaker": "Karlach",
          "text": "Someone wrong-footed him about me. Probably Zariel, somehow or other. Now Wyll's another of her victims.",
          "context": "NodeContext: Wyll died during the confrontation; Karlach is sad it came to that.",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "20",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "23": {
              "id": "23",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "If that's true, we've made a huge mistake.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "20",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "19": {
                  "id": "19",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "I'm afraid so. Maybe he would've listened if we'd reasoned with him a little longer. Or maybe we should've just outrun him. I don't know.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Wyll died during the confrontation; Karlach is sad it came to that.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "31": {
                      "id": "31",
                      "speaker": "",
                      "text": "",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "20",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "jump",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "7": {
              "id": "7",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What's done is done. He came after you; don't forget that.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "20",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "38": {
                  "id": "38",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "I never forget anything, unfortunately.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Wyll died during the confrontation; Karlach is sad it came to that.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {}
                }
              }
            },
            "12": {
              "id": "12",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "The Blade made his own decision - he was no victim.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "25": {
                  "id": "25",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "You say that. But he didn't come spoiling to kill a normal tiefling like me. He thought I was something I'm not.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Wyll died during the confrontation; Karlach is sad it came to that.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "20": {
                      "id": "20",
                      "speaker": "Karlach",
                      "text": "Hope he'll find the truth, now. And peace.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Wyll died during the confrontation; Karlach is sad it came to that.",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": true,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}